snippet.title: Amber Heard talks about her sexuality at the London Fields premiere
snippet.description:
On October 25th, Amber Heard attended the premiere of 'London Fields' in Los Angeles. In this interview with E!News she talks about her sexuality and says she never feels uncomfortable about it.
